title: Paul Ndicka Matam
text: Paul Heracles Ndicka Matam (born ) is a Cameroonian male <a href="Olympic%20weightlifting">weightlifter</a>, competing in the 56 kg category and representing Cameroon at international competitions. He participated at the <a href="2014%20Commonwealth%20Games">2014 Commonwealth Games</a> in the <a href="Weightlifting%20at%20the%202014%20Commonwealth%20Games%20%E2%80%93%20Men%27s%2056%20kg">56 kg event</a>.
